* * * [and this is (only) the beginning]
and this is (only) the beginning, the chaos, the shaded obstructed, which shows the space of the mixed presence. here. a lamp, a table, a piece of paper, the whole world in boxes, except for a few books. montale above all. the journey: an imprint of the silent sequence of words spoken into each other. one spoke to oneself beforehand - with the regret of the slightest thing. but yes, i still say. small things. water sounds, the night is governed and a loud penetrates through the empty spaces of the trees, as through the sleep of a white entropy.
